      "grammarNotes": "### Prosím — the magic word\n\n**Prosím** has multiple uses:\n1. **Please**: `Kávu, prosím.` — Coffee, please.\n2. **You're welcome**: After someone says `Děkuji`, reply `Prosím`.\n3. **Pardon?**: When you didn't hear, say `Prosím?`\n4. **Here you go**: Handing something over."
